Required Libraries

-Ruby


-Rails (installed via rubygems instead of apt)

  sudo gem install rails


-id3info command line program for getting tags from mp3 files

  sudo apt-get install libid3-3.8.3-dev


Initial Import


-Configure the database
  
  edit the development stanza of config/database.yml to point to your database


-Create the tables
 
  rake db:migrate

-Run scan_files on your directory

  script/scan_files.rb path-to-mp3s

